  "text": "In terms of postal sector, there is evident lack of papers, generally speaking. We find papers relating to universal postal service, some of them are: [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] and one paper which treated question of employees' stress level, as well as quality improvement in Serbian Post [CITATION_4] . According to the authors knowledge there are no papers concerning the implementation of ABC and ABC/M within the postal sector. Due to this fact, this paper contributes in the field of specific application of activity-based costing method.",
